## Key Techniques Summary

| Technique | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `window._setupAccount` exposure | Bridge between Playwright and React state |
| `page.evaluate()` | Run browser-context code from test scope |
| `page.addInitScript()` | Persist patches across page navigations |
| `anvil.snapshot()` / `anvil.revert()` | Idempotent test runs with chain state reset |
| `mock connector features` | Simulate errors (rejections, failures) without real wallets |
| `client.extend()` on viem | Custom methods (e.g., `syncDate`) on test clients |
| `mergeTests()` | Combine multiple fixture sets into one `test` function |
| `fullyParallel: false` | Enforce serial execution for chain-dependent tests |
